name: Courage Peace Love Ukraine
description:
We stand in solidarity with Ukraine in courage, peace, and love.

@Tery designed this glitch art video with licensed AI music to support the humanitarian efforts in Ukraine as part of the #Glitch4Ukraine showcase of glitch artists from the Tezos community.

This piece created by @Tery is part of the established contracts for Tezos donations to Ukrainian charities through the Glitch Art Showcase founded by @TerosEso in partnership with @rblbab @sonrefniocsid.

100% of the sales go to humanitarian efforts in Ukraine as indicated by the #Glitch4Ukraine description.
